dct_title_s: Topographical map showing the locations of the Sutro Tunnel and the Comstock Lode, State of Nevada, United States of America
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Oriented with north toward upper right. "March 1866." Includes two profiles: Longitudinal section of the Comstock Lode, and section of the Sutro Tunnel from its entrance to the Comstock Lode.
